name: Maze in the Deep
description:
Movement in-game and in the menu: WSAD or ARROWS and ENTER for buttons click.

Find the way out of the maze. Watch out for the sharks! If they spot you they will chase you. Don't starve yourself to death. Good luck!

"Maze in the Deep" has 3 levels of difficulty played one after another.
